{"title":"西昌小调","authors":["黄亚洲"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":7,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西昌小调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄亚洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西昌航天城的同志都是夸父后代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所不同者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸父弃其杖，化作桃林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而他们的手杖却始终直竖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为发射塔架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个太阳被他们囚禁着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被他们打扮着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳的升起不再根据格林威治时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而只服从中国国防部办公室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电话指示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的西昌人都是夸父后代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳在他们掌心里微微冒汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为让全国父老准时观赏日出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们检测液氢液氧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用一排电钮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反复针灸太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其时，在他们江南故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃花正红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们结伴踏青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只蜜蜂嗡嗡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哼西昌小调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被她们一下子掸飞了"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}